text:
In Settings -> Agent config:
1. The navigation bar gets weird and buggy and shows a scroll wheel
2. We don't need to show the text "Both API keys configured." - we should show the inputs if there are no API keys, but once the API keys are input, we don't need to show the text "Both API keys configured."
taskTitles: Fix navigation bar scroll/overflow bug on Settings Agent Config page
Hide API key inputs and status text once keys are configured
